14:26:16.684 [INFO] # Migrating to NORA MCP

14:26:16.684 [INFO] Use this workflow when a task asks you to mark existing notes for later migration into the NORA MCP vault.

14:26:16.684 [INFO] - Discover the exact migration marker shape under `../schemas/` before editing.
